implements AbstractAcscFaultResult
    An implementation of the model object 'Base Acsc Fault Result'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Cache Bus Sc Volt
    • Fault Point Amps
    • Fault Point V
    • ZFault
    • ZEq Fault
